snippet: Ana Ivanovic retired from tennis at age 29 Wednesday, ending a career in which she was ranked No. 1 in 2008 but can no longer play at the highest level because of injuries....
lead_paragraph: Ana Ivanovic retired from tennis at age 29 Wednesday, ending a career in which she was ranked No. 1 in 2008 but can no longer play at the highest level because of injuries.

headline.main: Former No. 1 Ana Ivanovic Retires From Tennis at 29
headline.print_headline: Former No. 1 Ana Ivanovic Retires From Tennis at 29
